data.title: Large Selection of Studio 7 Dance Apparel
data.meta_description: When looking for stylish and comfy Australian-made dancewear, check out our carefully selected range of Studio 7 apparel. Shop now, pay later. Free delivery over $120.

Note: This guide provides general sizing information, which can vary depending on style.

If your measurements are in between a size, we suggest suggest going the larger size to allow for growing room.

Adult XSml and Adult Sml are equivalent to Child 14 and Child 16 respectively.

Our shoe size charts are a guide only, they should be used as an aid and should NOT replace a personal fitting.

Dance shoes should fit firm with very little growing room to ensure the foot is well supported.

Charts are reflective of a ‘professional’ fit (a tighter fit) and are here to give you a general idea on sizing.
